{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to say that I don't where we-- where we found it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we stayed in-- in line to go to the toilets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in our room, we had a girl who was in charge of the showers, what we called showers, OK?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And being that she was in our room, she naturally gave us extra time to do things and when there was water and when there was heat, and you survived.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You did things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only remember, I think, once a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if we had in the morning, in the noon, or if we had in the morning and-- in morning and at noon, I think.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a piece of bread and what they called coffee or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then in Theresienstadt they had bread, and they had food we called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a cake-type-- type of thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Instead of bread, you could get that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what else was it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soups.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then later on, I worked in-- outside the ghetto in the gardens and in the fields, so we stole things and tried to feed us that way.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What type of work were you doing after you got better?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First I was working in-- they had like a-- a-- a repair shop for optical-- like glasses, right, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would-- was working in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yelinek ?] I worked for.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was an ops-- what do you call it, a optical doctor?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- optometrist, right?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, I had just actually two jobs I had in ghetto was what we called the [GERMAN] out at the gardens, in the fields.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was hard work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
